commit.message: Create scorecard.yml
Add bt-logindex blob kind
trivial: post release version bump
Release libjcat 0.2.1

Fix the installed tests
Most of the files needed for the installed tests aren't actually installed
and so the test suite doesn't work.  Adjust everything installed to let it
all work.
trivial: Add a note about blob order for maximum backwards compat
trivial: Show the sig-of-checksum results clearer on the CLI
Do not dedupe sig and sig-of-checksum when loading
trivial: post release version bump
Release libjcat 0.2.0

Allow verifying the checksum of a payload

This allows us to verify multi-gigabyte payloads without loading the entire
payload into memory.
trivial: Fix a tiny memory leak in the SHA1 self tests

trivial: Set G_TEST_SRCDIR to default if not already set

This means we can run the tests directly.
Allow creating and validating SHA512 checksums
Sprinkle __attribute__((nonnull)) to give a little more compile-time safety
Add support for verifying firmware transparency checkpoints
trivial: Fix CI

Add various bitcounting functions for future use
